{"tid":1840218,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★麥當勞發聲明，指武漢、鄂州、黃岡、潛江和仙桃市的門店都已於24日起關閉。","createTime":"2020-01-24T18:11:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T09:55:31.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"74af7867bc7210b85d1a32d10d0350a7b5c7e6ee","tid":1840218,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:11:00.000Z","msg":"0130 麥當勞發聲明，指武漢、鄂州、黃岡、潛江和仙桃市的所有門店都已於周五（24日）起暫時關閉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200125/bkn-20200125000006766-0125_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200125%2Fbkn-20200125000006766-0125_00822_001.html&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT6HDOfwBZUVptSzBKRgi4hA%3D&h=537d5927\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200125/bkn-20200125000006766-0125_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4902536f788c3f220edd6ef391fdfdcff71c7cee","tid":1840218,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:11:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f0368d9e24d3f0472144a0123c5199d26985ff9","tid":1840218,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:17:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真 RIP"},{"pid":"f0a187da1b9aac5015a371b9bbb440c2d5e06798","tid":1840218,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:19:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n天滅中共"},{"pid":"8b92902ef840fe49396bc23519aafd8c8ea5cb7e","tid":1840218,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:52:42.000Z","msg":"致四大醫護專業工會<br />\n<br />\n近日致命武漢肺炎肆虐全球，世界各地的政府均已實行嚴謹的防疫措施。唯獨香港特區政府對關口的防疫工作置之不理，令大量懷疑感染新型冠狀病毒的外來患者湧入香港。<br />\n<br />\n港府在防疫工作上力度不足，以及後知後覺的態度，直接令醫護界工作壓力及感染機會大增，甚至需要以抽生死籤來決定進入隔離病房的醫護名單。在未有任何確切治療的方案下，此致命的疫症絕大機會令2003 年沙士事件中，醫護人員因受感染而死亡的傷痛事件重現，再次勾起港人的悲痛回憶。<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，一眾熱心的市民已於2020年1月24日零晨，在《香港地投票》應用程式內發起了一項投票事項。投票只開放予香港境內市民，亦以一系列的措施盡力達至一人一票，其內容如下：<br />\n<br />\n議題：支唔支持醫護大罷工<br />\n投票開放時間：一個月<br />\n截至2020年1月25日零晨為止，24小時內已有1117名香港市民投票，當中約97%支持香港醫護人員罷工，約2%反對及2張廢票。<br />\n<br />\n《香港地投票》應用程式作為一個投票平台，致力為不同民生或政制議題及各種工業行動提供民意基礎。現來信各醫護工會團體，藉此轉達市民的意見。考慮到醫護人員有其專業，亦關乎病人及其家屬的權益。醫護人員罷工與否的決定將完全留待醫護界自行決定，此函只供各大機構作民意參考之用。<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票<br />\n謹啟<br />\n2020-01-25<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkvote.org/Letter/20200125.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkvote.org%2FLetter%2F20200125.pdf&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT6HDOfwBZUVptSzBKRgi4hA%3D&h=af12d159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkvote.org/Letter/20200125.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n有勞大家幫我forword 俾醫護工會同各醫護知<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"f25d866ed47840b853301a211843448b5e20c200","tid":1840218,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:52:46.000Z","msg":"做麥難民都冇行"},{"pid":"5c9c810be341c6ef4b04f8e323d8ecf50902057f","tid":1840218,"uid":318928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:53:07.000Z","msg":"要快！必須要有612咁大型  已經冇退路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1840260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1840260</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5ac897caba1be4487f5454935ae1b1aaba148828","tid":1840218,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T03:34:10.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"216263c73bc848e3808f32d33bdc816a8d08b471","tid":1840218,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:55:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}